#1765

TORAY OPTICAL STORAGE SOLUTIONS SHOWS NEXT-GENERATION
PHASE CHANGE OPTICAL PRODUCTS AT AIIM

SAN FRANCISCO - Feb. 21, 1995 - Toray Optical Storage Solutions will be
showing its extensive line of new phase change optical storage systems
at AIIM, Booth No. 5377, April 11-13, in San Francisco.

