STARFISH SOFTWARE SHIPS SIDEKICK FOR WINDOWS 2.0

SAN FRANCISCO  - Feb. 21, 1995 -  Starfish Software announced that it
has begun shipping to major resellers nationwide a major upgrade of
Sidekick for Windows, the best-selling slimware personal organizer.

Sidekick for Windows 2.0 -- with 101 new and improved features -- is
