#1778

100% OF HACKERS FAILED TO BREAK INTO ONE
INTERNET SITE PROTECTED BY SIDEWINDER(TM)

New world-wide challenge issued

ROSEVILLE, Minn. - Feb. 23, 1995 - On Nov. 7, 1994, Secure Computing
issued a challenge to the world's hackers ... and they all failed.

The publicly announced and easily accessible Sidewinder Challenge
invited hackers and information warriors world-wide to test their
skills, using any and all techniques: in short, there were no rules.
