#1780

AST GIVES CUSTOMERS TOP BILLING IN MOVE TO WINDOWS 95

IRVINE, Calif. - Feb. 23, 1995 - AST Computer predicts big box-office
results for Microsoft(R) Windows(R) 95 as it takes a "Sneak Preview"
on the road to show customers how to make the most of the new operating
system that is sure to become a classic.

To ensure the customer is the winner of this blockbuster debut, AST has
