APPLE, IBM, MOTOROLA PRESENT THE 'POWERPC PARK' AT CEBIT '95

MUNICH, Germany, and PARIS, Feb. 23 - Apple, IBM and Motorola will
present a broad range of hardware and software solutions, applications,
operating systems and development tools for the PowerPC microprocessor
in a unique park setting at CeBIT '95 (March 8-15, Hanover, Germany).

The PowerPC Park will feature more than 60 independent software and
