#1785

LOTUS SHIPS LOTUS NOTES DESKTOP

CAMBRIDGE, Mass., Feb. 23 - Lotus Development Corp. today announced it
has begun shipments of Lotus Notes Desktop, the company's new Notes run-
time client announced last month.

Designed for organizations that want a cost-effective way to deploy
corporate-wide Notes applications Notes Desktop allows users to run any
Notes application to which they have access rights. The product can be
used remotely or connected to a LAN.
info: tel. 800-872-3387 ext. A600
